<node id="A Christmas Carol">
  <data key="d0">A Christmas Carol</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Christmas Carol is a novella written by Charles Dickens, first published in 1843, telling the story of Ebenezer Scrooge and his transformation.&lt;SEP&gt;A Christmas Carol is a literary work referenced as part of Project Gutenberg's collection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-194cd9680f4967f48bea89678f7ece21&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43</data>
