<node id="Ghost of Christmas Past">
  <data key="d0">Ghost of Christmas Past</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Ghost of Christmas Past is one of three spirits in "A Christmas Carol," who reveals Scrooge's past to evoke reflection and change.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Past is a spirit who guides Scrooge through memories, appearing with changing forms and emphasizing the importance of recollection and reflection.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Past is a spirit that shows Scrooge his former self and past experiences, prompting reflections on his life choices.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Past is a spectral being that reminds Scrooge of his past experiences and emotions associated with Christmas.</data>
