<node id="Cratchit Family">
  <data key="d0">Cratchit Family</data>
  <data key="d1">family</data>
  <data key="d2">The Cratchit family includes several members, including Bob, Martha, Tiny Tim, Peter, and two younger siblings, showcasing their interactions during Christmas.&lt;SEP&gt;The Cratchit Family includes Bob, Mrs. Cratchit, Tiny Tim, and the other young Cratchits, who celebrate Christmas together, highlighting their closeness despite financial struggles.&lt;SEP&gt;The Cratchit Family consists of Bob, Mrs. Cratchit, Tiny Tim, and their children, showcasing strong familial bonds and love.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7e2e7ebcc19a53b399dc03aded4743e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d4b58de5429cd1261370c231c8673e8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-503f0bfa5453467c7c61d160a3540eca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0f459f5af1c3a5e0b92cbe4ee48b77b</data>
