<edge source="Scrooge's Nephew" target="Scrooge">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Scrooge and his nephew share a family relationship, with differing views on wealth and the meaning of Christmas.&lt;SEP&gt;Scrooge and his nephew have a familial relationship characterized by disagreement regarding the celebration and significance of Christmas.&lt;SEP&gt;Scrooge recognizes his Nephew's laughter and finds joy in the familial connection during the Spirit's visit.&lt;SEP&gt;Scrooge's nephew fosters a light-hearted atmosphere in the gathering, contributing to Scrooge's eventual openness and holiday spirit.&lt;SEP&gt;Scrooge's nephew contrasts his joyful demeanor with Scrooge's grumpy attitude while expressing concern for his uncle's well-being.</data>
  <data key="d9">contrast,contrasting perspectives,disagreement,family connection,family relation,family relationship,festive spirit,joy</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-74e2466de2f67fd710ef2f20c0a8d9e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-773d0df1dd25c356f7b771d780583e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91614df5cb74cbe5e109a338a82041e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43c9bee23adfa77aa9dedd22401bba7d</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1765980076</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Scrooge's Nephew" target="Christmas">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Scrooge's nephew advocates for the positive aspects of Christmas, in stark opposition to Scrooge's negativity.&lt;SEP&gt;Scrooge's nephew defends the concept of Christmas against Scrooge's disparaging remarks, highlighting its importance.</data>
  <data key="d9">celebration,defense,positivity</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-773d0df1dd25c356f7b771d780583e09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd</data>
